title: Chicken Sandwich Taste Test + Real Or Fake News + Bobby's Mailbag
itunes:title: Chicken Sandwich Taste Test + Real Or Fake News + Bobby's Mailbag
description:
Lunchbox decides which chicken sandwich is better....Popeye's or Chick-Fil-A. Bobby reads recent news stories and lets the crew decide which ones are real and which ones are fake. Bobby opens up the mailbag to address a listener's first date concerns.
